TweetWall
---------

TweetWall is an iPad app to display a slideshow of tweets based on an hashtag (or any search query).
Tweets are shown one at a time. It's great for any event using an external projector/TV or as a PhotoFrame.

This project has been done during #iOSDevCamp (http://iosdevcamp.org), Aug 20-22, 2010.

Initial contributors are:

Code:
- Christian Sanz (chrissanz at gmail)
- Stefan (stefan at makeliferock dot com) 
- Xavier Damman (xdamman at gmail)

Design:
- Joshua Mauldin (hello at joshuamauldin.com>
- Amir Khella (akhella at gmail)


